    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/depuy-synthes-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged; the ASTM F1717 single-configuration limitation is mitigated by the direct regulatory equivalence of the test protocol and the conservative nature of the compression-bending load case. All QoI validation metrics satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds. The credibility body of evidence, including bench test data from two independent laboratories, supports acceptance of the FEA model for the stated COU. Note: the bound claim references supporting evidence discussed in the simulation report narrative but the formal provenance link was not captured in this package.",
